1.2
log
@Update to 2.05. This version is completely rewritten from 1.005.
@
text
@HTML::FromText converts plain text to HTML. There are a handful
of options that shape the conversion. There is a utility function,
text2html, that's exported by default. This function is simply a
short-cut to the Object Oriented interface.
@


1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@d1 4
a4 5
The module marks up plain text as HTML.  By default it converts
HTML metacharacters into the corresponding entities.  More sophisticated
transformations, such as splitting the text into paragraphs or
marking up bulleted lists, can be carried out by setting the
appropriate options.
@


